command: SELECT intervals."INTERVAL"  AS "intervals.interval", dampcloud_visual_scores.NAME  AS "dampcloud_visual_scores.name", COUNT(DISTINCT dampcloud_visual_scores."_ID" ) AS "dampcloud_visual_scores.count" FROM DASH100451.INTERVALS  AS intervals FULL OUTER JOIN DASH100451."DAMP-CLOUD"  AS dampcloud ON (substr((TO_CHAR(TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(TIMESTAMP('1970-01-01-00.00.00') + (CAST(DAYS(to_timestamp(dampcloud.YEAR || '-'|| dampcloud.MONTH || '-' || dampcloud.DAY || ' ' || dampcloud.HOUR || ':' || dampcloud.MINUTE || ':' || dampcloud.SECOND, 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS') ) - DAYS(TIMESTAMP('1970-01-01')) AS INTEGER) * 86400 + MIDNIGHT_SECONDS(to_timestamp(dampcloud.YEAR || '-'|| dampcloud.MONTH || '-' || dampcloud.DAY || ' ' || dampcloud.HOUR || ':' || dampcloud.MINUTE || ':' || dampcloud.SECOND, 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS') ) - MOD(CAST(DAYS(to_timestamp(dampcloud.YEAR || '-'|| dampcloud.MONTH || '-' || dampcloud.DAY || ' ' || dampcloud.HOUR || ':' || dampcloud.MINUTE || ':' || dampcloud.SECOND, 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS') ) - DAYS(TIMESTAMP('1970-01-01')) AS INTEGER) * 86400 + MIDNIGHT_SECONDS(to_timestamp(dampcloud.YEAR || '-'|| dampcloud.MONTH || '-' || dampcloud.DAY || ' ' || dampcloud.HOUR || ':' || dampcloud.MINUTE || ':' || dampcloud.SECOND, 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS') ), 60 * 15)) SECONDS, 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI') || ':00'), 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI')),12,5)) = (intervals."INTERVAL") FULL OUTER JOIN DASH100451."DAMP-CLOUD_VISUAL_SCORES"  AS dampcloud_visual_scores ON (dampcloud_visual_scores."_ID") = (dampcloud."_ID") and (substr((TO_CHAR(TIMESTAMP(TO_CHAR(TIMESTAMP('1970-01-01-00.00.00') + (CAST(DAYS(to_timestamp(dampcloud.YEAR || '-'|| dampcloud.MONTH || '-' || dampcloud.DAY || ' ' || dampcloud.HOUR || ':' || dampcloud.MINUTE || ':' || dampcloud.SECOND, 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS') ) - DAYS(TIMESTAMP('1970-01-01')) AS INTEGER) * 86400 + MIDNIGHT_SECONDS(to_timestamp(dampcloud.YEAR || '-'|| dampcloud.MONTH || '-' || dampcloud.DAY || ' ' || dampcloud.HOUR || ':' || dampcloud.MINUTE || ':' || dampcloud.SECOND, 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS') ) - MOD(CAST(DAYS(to_timestamp(dampcloud.YEAR || '-'|| dampcloud.MONTH || '-' || dampcloud.DAY || ' ' || dampcloud.HOUR || ':' || dampcloud.MINUTE || ':' || dampcloud.SECOND, 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS') ) - DAYS(TIMESTAMP('1970-01-01')) AS INTEGER) * 86400 + MIDNIGHT_SECONDS(to_timestamp(dampcloud.YEAR || '-'|| dampcloud.MONTH || '-' || dampcloud.DAY || ' ' || dampcloud.HOUR || ':' || dampcloud.MINUTE || ':' || dampcloud.SECOND, 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS') ), 60 * 15)) SECONDS, 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI') || ':00'), 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI')),12,5)) = (intervals."INTERVAL") GROUP BY intervals."INTERVAL" ,dampcloud_visual_scores.NAME ORDER BY 1
